Change only happens when each does their part. Nik helps your users do theirs.

Our impact optimisation lab combines the knowledge and practice of applied social and behavioral sciences, product and service design and business consulting in order to achieve a thorough understanding of the barriers and triggers of behavior. Such understanding allows us to design cost-effective strategies to improve the ethical adoption of behaviors that are key to impact.

Nik can help you...
... increase your patients adherence to treatment;
... foster your insurance consumers' adoption of preventive measures;
... improve your employee's adoption of DE&I policies;
... enhance your users' adoption of your greentech solution or circular economy initiative;
